Definition: hormone secreted by the isles of Langerhans in the pancreas
Example: regulates storage of glycogen in the liver and accelerates oxidation of sugar in cells
Synonyms: hormone, noun, substance, hypoglycemic_agent, secreted, by, the, isles, of, Langerhans, in, pancreas, regulates, storage, glycogen, liver, and, accelerates, oxidation, sugar, cells
Category: noun.body
